<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4634667>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 10. Roboastra leonis sp. nov. (CASIZ 097577). A, scanning electron micrograph of the oral tube, scale bar = 2 mm. The drawing shows the oral tube opened and the presence of a pair of elongate pouches opening into the digestive system. B, detail of the right elongate pouche, scale bar = 1 mm. Abbreviations: ep, elongate pouches; lc, labial cuticle; m, mouth; ot, oral tube." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4634667/files/figure.png" .

